posts.post_title: WTB - portraits I need to finish out the A, B, C, D & E's
posts.post_content:
I'm looking to make some progress on my T206 portrait set. I'd like to try to finish out the A's, B's, C's, D's, and E's. Here are the portraits that I still need:


Ames
Armbruster
Bender
Bowerman
Brashear
Bridwell (no cap)
Carr
Cassidy
Chance (red)
Chesbro
Coles
Collins, Eddie
Collins, Jimmy
Crandall (with cap)
Criger
Dahlen (Boston)
Dessau
Doolin
Doyle
Durham
Egan
Elberfield (New York)


CONDITION: grade doesn't matter too much to me as long as it's not missing chunks, no paper loss on the front (minimal paper loss on the back is fine).

Prefer SGC graded but I'll take raw, PSA, or SGC.

Please provide scans/photos and price to: [URL="bayouzach@bellsouth.net"]bayouzach@bellsouth.net[/URL]

Thanks,
Zach
